                to raise your family, as well as for investment. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The surroundings and neighborhood of Shaganappi are extremely family-friendly and
                welcoming, proving to be a very healthy and wholesome location for a couple or a family. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Shaganappi has a variety of types of homes â€“ from century old homes to ultra-modern
                structures built thanks to the active redevelopment that is happening in environs. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">One of the best features of Shaganappi is that it offers almost the same facilities as the
                more upscale Scarboro, but at more affordable price.</p>

